p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870580/extras/dbc7fb32ce528a7aafc5e2b91d8686e7.avif?t=1773587320\" width=600 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870580/extras/306fe90a62fe75199e2aa8e34446e456.poster.avif?t=1773587320\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870580/extras/306fe90a62fe75199e2aa8e34446e456.webm?t=1773587320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870580/extras/306fe90a62fe75199e2aa8e34446e456.mp4?t=1773587320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock challenge modes, characters, items and more, ensuring endless replayability. Create a strong enough build and you can take on the Infinite Desert and push it to its limits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACTIVE SUPPORT AND EXPANSION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Update 1.5 is now available!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Procedural character collection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Class based meta progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Optimized for PC and Steam Deck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Auto-saved progress with Cloud saves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Continued expansion and improvement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Physically simulated emergent interactions and fluid controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Objective-based gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Endless Mode with Friend Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collections and challenges for items and enemies</p></li></ul>",
